---
title: Goat's Cheese Aubergine with Chermoula Freekeh and Cucumber & Mint Salad
description: Freekeh, made from durum wheat, makes a great replacement for rice in this deliciously simple vegetarian recipe. Once cooked, freekeh has a natural al dente bite and nutty texture which works brilliantly with silky aubergine, crunchy cucumber and creamy grilled goat’s cheese. Packed with veggie goodness and fresh, delicious flavours, we’ve got a feeling that this is about to become your new go-to recipe!
